  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/99d9754cd6b487fe25082808a55fb3d7.poster.avif?t=1724437192\" width=616 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/99d9754cd6b487fe25082808a55fb3d7.webm?t=1724437192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Oberty</strong> is a minimalist shape-blending puzzle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Black + Black = White</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/4c335b01d00b3c742a237d09fad5efa8.poster.avif?t=1724437192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/4c335b01d00b3c742a237d09fad5efa8.webm?t=1724437192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/4c335b01d00b3c742a237d09fad5efa8.mp4?t=1724437192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Rotate and blend cards with XOR rule: \"Black + Black = White\".<br>Oberty gives you a few tiles with simple geometric shapes, choose some, rotate and combine tiles to reach target shape.<br><br>• 200+ puzzles to complete<br>• Meditative<br>• Minimal<br>• Monochromatic<br>• Atmospheric original soundtrack<br>• Inclusive color schemes for people with visual impairment<br>• Level editor, create and share you cards with friends<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVEL EDITOR</h2>Create your own unique level-cards, share it to your friends by sending picture. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/bcb2623376cc7683693e45a75ee598a1.poster.avif?t=1724437192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/bcb2623376cc7683693e45a75ee598a1.webm?t=1724437192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/bcb2623376cc7683693e45a75ee598a1.mp4?t=1724437192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To play level simply load it from picture of level-card.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/7b1285b130e83d0fa2cac70a56267622.poster.avif?t=1724437192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/7b1285b130e83d0fa2cac70a56267622.webm?t=1724437192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/7b1285b130e83d0fa2cac70a56267622.mp4?t=1724437192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/99d9754cd6b487fe25082808a55fb3d7.poster.avif?t=1724437192\" width=616 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/99d9754cd6b487fe25082808a55fb3d7.webm?t=1724437192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Oberty</strong> is a minimalist shape-blending puzzle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Black + Black = White</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/4c335b01d00b3c742a237d09fad5efa8.poster.avif?t=1724437192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/4c335b01d00b3c742a237d09fad5efa8.webm?t=1724437192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/4c335b01d00b3c742a237d09fad5efa8.mp4?t=1724437192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Rotate and blend cards with XOR rule: \"Black + Black = White\".<br>Oberty gives you a few tiles with simple geometric shapes, choose some, rotate and combine tiles to reach target shape.<br><br>• 200+ puzzles to complete<br>• Meditative<br>• Minimal<br>• Monochromatic<br>• Atmospheric original soundtrack<br>• Inclusive color schemes for people with visual impairment<br>• Level editor, create and share you cards with friends<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVEL EDITOR</h2>Create your own unique level-cards, share it to your friends by sending picture. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469570/extras/bcb2623376cc7683693e45a75ee598a1.po